        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                     Radius Searching. There is always a 'BOSS' cop, which is used to show the area where are our gangsters number is the highest.
                </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                   Added some base nodes, an algorithm calculate the distance between the BOSS cop and the nearest base node and then send the actual cop to the nearest sector if it is more valuable than the BOSS cop sector.
                </para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>
                   Added some trivial functions, a gangster won't be followed by two cops, and a sector search function which gives us the number of the gangsters per sectors.
